<TR>
<TD>&nbsp;<FONT FACE="Verdana,
Arial, Helvetica"
SIZE="2" color="red"><B>

Aladdin costs its customers Millions

</B></FONT>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<TABLE WIDTH="389" BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=6>
<TR>
<TD>
<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="2">
<p> 
<FONT COLOR="gray" size=-2><B>contributed byWar3z Dud3</B>
</FONT>
<BR>
<FONT COLOR="BLACK">

Customers of Aladdin Software Systems are crying foul claiming that
the company does not respond to security problems with its products.
Aladdin manufactures hardware dongles to prevent software piracy.
Aladdin customers are claiming that the HASP series is widely known to
contain security flaws but that the company refuses to fix the flaws
costing the software publishers millions of dollars in pirated
software. 

<p>
<a
href="http://www.globes.co.il/cgi-bin/Serve_Archive_Arena/pages/English/1.4.1.2/19990202/1">Israel's
Business Arena</a><br>
<p>
</FONT> 
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>
<!-- End Day -->
